The paper is about a deep learning-based recommender system, which is a subfield of information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of deep learning also suggests a potential connection to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the implementation of the algorithms using Tensorflow indicates a focus on deep learning (cs.DL).
